105
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,840
Once I'm done with these two days,

106
00:05:24,610 --> 00:05:25,980
I'll rush over to find you.

107
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:39,120
The guys at the dock saw Yi Qiuting

108
