133
00:06:53,250 --> 00:06:54,680
Ma'am, how are you feeling?

134
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:55,710
I'm about to give birth.

135
00:06:56,090 --> 00:06:58,330
Please, help me!

136
00:06:58,580 --> 00:07:00,740
