143
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:14,740
[Engagement]

144
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:14,820
A few years ago, I met Qiuting once.

145
00:07:14,990 --> 00:07:17,700
At that time, I found he had an extraordinary presence.

146
00:07:17,900 --> 00:07:18,730
I never expected

147
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:21,300
that he would become my son-in-law today.

148
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,240
Chief Duan,

149
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:26,350
from now on, I'll entrust this kid to you.

150
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:28,040
Please make sure to guide him well.

151
00:07:28,670 --> 00:07:31,890
Qiuting is a bit hot-headed in his youth.

152
00:07:32,340 --> 00:07:33,290
He doesn't even

153
00:07:33,310 --> 00:07:35,680
respect me as his father now.

154
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:38,250
We are a family now, so there's no need to be so polite.

155
00:07:38,780 --> 00:07:42,920
I heard that you're planning to build a railway in Jiangsu and Zhejiang.

156
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:51,830
Congratulations on the union of the Yi family and the Duan family.

157
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:52,300
Please.

158
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:54,460
Thank you. Please, make yourselves comfortable.

159
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,909
-This way, please.
-Let's go.

160
00:07:57,530 --> 00:07:59,909
Jinyao, this time, it's all up to you.

161
00:07:59,930 --> 00:08:00,930
