167
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:13,190
to help you become the head of the Duan family.

168
00:08:20,450 --> 00:08:21,540
This way.

169
00:08:23,650 --> 00:08:25,320
Young Marshal, there's no need to worry.

170
00:08:25,850 --> 00:08:27,190
Miss Zhao is with our brothers.

171
00:08:29,180 --> 00:08:31,400
